## Why Next.js App Router?

Next.js 13+'s App Router clearly separates server and client components, significantly improving initial load performance.

## Tech Stack

- **Next.js 16** - App Router framework
- **CSS Modules** - Scoped styling
- **Vercel** - Automatic CI/CD deployment

## Benefits of CSS Modules

You can build powerful UIs with plain Vanilla CSS without Tailwind. CSS Modules prevent class name collisions and enable component-level style management.

```css
.card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
}
```

## Performance Optimizations

- Automatic image optimization with `next/image`
- IntersectionObserver via custom `useScrollReveal` hook
- Font optimization: Google Fonts loaded via Next.js font API
